short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AI2sql is an AI-powered SQL generator that lets you write your SQL in seconds.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Build SQL queries easily in your browser: AI2sql Chrome Extension generates an SQL query based on your input. With this simple and useful tool you'll be able to generate the query quickly from your web browser.
